[[File:Lanthus chathead.png|left]]
'''Lanthus''' is the manager of the [[Castle Wars]] [[minigame]] and stands in the lobby. Besides exchanging [[Castle wars ticket]]s for various prizes at the [[Castle Wars Ticket Exchange]], Lanthus also informs players when a game has ended and tells players new to Castle Wars about the game. [[Postie Pete]] will at times appear in the Castle Wars lobby and hold a brief conversation with Lanthus.

He can also be contacted via the [[NPC Contact]] spell to know when the next game of Castle Wars starts and how many players are on each team.

If you use an [[Ava's device]] on him, he will offer to collect your ranged ammunition.

